===Etymology===
First attested in the late 14th century. From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|acusacion}} (French {{m|fr|accusation}}), from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|accūsātiō||accusation, indictment}}, from {{m|la|accūsō||blame, accuse}}. More at {{m|en|accuse}}.

